Package zserio.runtime.array

This package contains array wrapper which is used for mapping of all zserio arrays.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ArrayElement
    Common interface for all array elements.
    ArrayElement.IntegralArrayElement
    Interface for elements of integral arrays.
    ArrayTraits
    Interface for array traits.
    ArrayTraits.IntegralArrayTraits
    Interface for integral array traits.
    ElementFactory<E>
    Interface used to construct elements from the bit stream.
    OffsetChecker
    Interface used to check array indexed offsets during reading/writing of arrays from/to bit stream.
    OffsetInitializer
    Interface used to set array indexed offsets during offset initialization.
    PackableElementFactory<E>
    Interface used to construct packable elements from the bit stream.
    PackedArrayTraits
    Interface for packed array traits.
    RawArray
    Interface for classes which holds raw array.
